main.bio: Hey, my name is Pyae Naing. I have recently graduated from San Francisco State University in May 2020, with B.S in Computer Science and Minor in Mathmatics. I design, and create database and functions that are fast and high performance for the backend. I have done projects in in Java, C++, Javascript, MySQL, MongoDB and Node.JS. I am dedicated worker, problem solver, team player and would love to prove it to you.
